column1: Source: USDA Branded Food Products Database Release July 2018 Software v.3.9.5 2018-08-15
Nutrient data for: CADBURY CHOCOLATE BAR, UNPREPARED, GTIN: 07622300697556
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

Ingredients: MILK, sugar, glucose syrup, cocoa butter, vegetable fats (palm, shea), glucose-fructose syrup, cocoa mass, whey powder (from MILK), whole MILK powder, skimmed MILK powder, emulsifiers (E442, E471, SOYA lecithin), salt, MILK fat, molasses, flavourings, sodium carbonate, humectant (glycerol), acidity regulator (sodium bicarbonate), stabilizer (invertase), colour (paprika extract). Family milk chocolate contains: milk solids 20% minimum, cocoa solids 20% minimum.Milk chocolate contains: milk solids 14% minimum, cocoa solids 25% minimum.Contains vegetable fats in addition to cocoa butter. MAY CONTAIN NUTS. Date available: 11/10/2017 Date last updated by company: 12/15/2016
